      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "POUND KEEPING (4) has a terrific record here with two wins and one placing from three starts. Scored by 2.25 lengths last time (29.96) in a OPEN over 520m at this track. Rates a leading player. NANGAR ONYX (1) was out of the placings last time when sixth at this track (30.93) but did record second best time of the card when winning five back. Form here at the trip sound including four wins. Has the ability to give this a shake. GARRITTY (3) tends to take a while to wind up, running on to place two back before spotting a start latest and finishing on strongly into second (30.30) in a Grade 4/5 at this track. Has a good record at this journey. Winning chance. ASTON FREDDIE (6) gets a chance to redeem an unplaced effort here last start.",
